# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs9.rpy:17
translate chinese welchs9_8a627f13:

    # sst "Oh fuck, yes. All the time."
    sst "哦操，没错。一直都是。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs9.rpy:18
translate chinese welchs9_b013619c:

    # sst "The world is so fucked up in a hundred different ways."
    sst "这世界在无数方面都他妈的烂透了。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs9.rpy:20
translate chinese welchs9_08cef2a4:

    # sst "I worry about the environment. That the Earth is getting hotter and we're just going to burn away."
    sst "我担心环境问题。地球越来越热，我们迟早会被烤焦。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs9.rpy:21
translate chinese welchs9_06f365fa:

    # sst "That storms are going to continue to get worse."
    sst "风暴会越来越猛烈。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs9.rpy:22
translate chinese welchs9_989b947e:

    # sst "That waters are going to rise and swallow the shorelines."
    sst "海平面会上升，吞没海岸线。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs9.rpy:24
translate chinese welchs9_43854413:

    # sst "Worse than that, I worry about our government."
    sst "更糟的是，我担心我们的政府。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs9.rpy:25
translate chinese welchs9_84ae5b06:

    # sst "That the rich are going to continue getting richer, until they enslave every one of us under their capitalist thumbs."
    sst "担心富人会变得越来越富，直到他们用资本主义的铁腕奴役我们所有人。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs9.rpy:26
translate chinese welchs9_85a48cee:

    # sst "That religious interest groups are going to continue taking over and driving out anybody who is different than what they consider right."
    sst "担心宗教利益集团会继续扩张，驱逐任何与他们所谓“正确”标准不符的人。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs9.rpy:28
translate chinese welchs9_22d3a2ec:

    # sst "I worry that somebody is going to come into my classroom and shoot me or my students."
    sst "我担心有人会闯进我的教室，朝我或我的学生开枪。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs9.rpy:30
translate chinese welchs9_1666ed17:

    # sst "And what I worry about the most is that half this country seems to think that all of this is okay and normal."
    sst "而我最担心的，是这个国家的一半人似乎觉得这一切都无所谓，甚至很正常。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs9.rpy:32
translate chinese welchs9_0ab77d75:

    # sst "So yeah, I have a lot of worries."
    sst "所以，是的，我有很多担忧。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs9.rpy:34
translate chinese welchs9_291aef47:

    # sst "I do what I can though. Everything I can."
    sst "但我尽我所能。竭尽所能。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs9.rpy:35
translate chinese welchs9_1ae24bc9:

    # sst "I put a lot of myself into making the world a better place in any way I can."
    sst "我倾注了大量心血，试图用任何可能的方式让世界变得更好。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs9.rpy:37
translate chinese welchs9_58a74a6f:

    # sst "But I know that I can only do so much."
    sst "但我知道，我能做的终究有限。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs9.rpy:39
translate chinese welchs9_b4163dcf:

    # sst "So I do my best to let go of the things that I cannot change."
    sst "所以我尽力去放下那些无法改变的事。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs9.rpy:40
translate chinese welchs9_a20ffdb7:

    # pc "It's really very admirable."
    pc "这真的非常值得钦佩。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs9.rpy:41
translate chinese welchs9_4f5378c6:

    # sst "I'm glad you don't think I'm {i}too{/i} crazy."
    sst "很高兴你不觉得我{i}太{/i}疯狂。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs9.rpy:42
translate chinese welchs9_92994cd5:

    # pc "Nah, I like the level of crazy that you are."
    pc "不，我喜欢你这种程度的疯狂。"

